      "settings": {
        "heading": "Why Choose the PostJoy GT16?",
        "heading_size": "title-md",
        "heading_alignment": "text-left md:items-end md:flex-row",
        "heading_tag": "h2",
        "subheading": "",
        "description": "<p>Meet the PostJoy GT16 — a compact electric dirt bike built for riders who want more power, more control, and more freedom on every ride.<br/><br/>With a <strong>3000W</strong> peak motor and up to <strong>70Nm</strong> of torque, the GT16 delivers instant acceleration, confident climbing power, and a thrilling top speed of up to 40 MPH. From dirt trails and gravel roads to steep 45° climbs, this “Micro Beast” is ready to take on the terrain.<br/><br/>The <strong>48V 25Ah</strong> removable battery gives you up to 100 miles of PAS range, so you can ride farther without constantly worrying about your next charge. Full suspension, hydraulic disc brakes, and 16\" x 3.0\" off-road tires work together to keep the ride stable, smooth, and controlled.<br/><br/>Finished with NFC smart unlock and a bold skull-motif headlight, the GT16 is more than an e-bike. It is a high-performance electric dirt bike built for adventure.</p>",
        "button_label": "",
        "button_link": "",
        "button_external": false,
        "button_icon": true,
        "highlighted_text": "scribble",
        "highlighted_scribble": "basic-underline",
