    "yg_image_with_text_list_KQztzz": {
      "type": "yg-image-with-text-list",
      "blocks": {
        "item_FQddzf": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/3._61fc182d-616f-408a-9f18-9a818b57e62d.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p><strong>3000W Peak Motor</strong><br/>Explosive Power for Dirt, Hills, and Daily Rides</p>",
            "content": "<p>The GT16’s 3000W peak motor delivers strong acceleration, responsive throttle feel, and up to 200Nm of torque. Whether you are climbing steep hills, cutting through loose gravel, or cruising open paths, the GT16 gives you the power to ride with confidence.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_Y77eFc": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/BATTERY_25AH.png",
            "image_pos": "right",
            "title": "<p><strong>48V 25Ah</strong> Removable Battery<br/>Ride Farther. Charge Easier.</p>",
            "content": "<p>Go longer between charges with a high-capacity 48V 25Ah battery. Enjoy up to 100 miles of PAS range, then remove the battery for convenient charging at home, in the office, or wherever your next adventure begins.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_6M3dHz": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 96,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/2_884a1e86-d2cc-4a32-9d2b-db57bf7cd86e.jpg",
            "image_pos": "left",
            "title": "<p><strong>Full Suspension System</strong><br/>Smooth Control on Rough Terrain</p>",
            "content": "<p>The GT16’s full suspension system is built to absorb bumps, drops, and trail vibration. A high-travel front hydraulic fork and rear monoshock help keep the ride planted and stable, giving you more comfort, more traction, and more control when the terrain gets rough.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_VNaYcH": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "item_margin_top": 60,
            "item_margin_bottom": 60,
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/4_3a5a80aa-3e82-41dd-ac64-45c885515101.jpg",
            "image_pos": "right",
            "title": "<p><strong>16\" x 3.0\" Off-Road Tires</strong><br/>Confident Grip on Dirt, Gravel, and Pavement</p>",
            "content": "<p>The GT16 rides on wide 16\" x 3.0\" motorcycle-style tires with aggressive tread for dependable traction. From dirt trails and gravel roads to city pavement, these tires help deliver stability, grip, and off-road confidence.</p>",
            "param_title_1": "",
            "param_content_1": "",
            "param_title_2": "",
            "param_content_2": ""
          }
        },
        "item_zmQHGy": {
