            "title": "<p>Choose the <strong>Right Mode</strong> for Every Ride</p>",
            "content": "<p>5 Ways to Ride<br/>Throttle, cruise, walk assist, pedal assist, or traditional bike mode — switch easily to match your road, range, and riding style.</p>",
